      <title>印度股市现金周转率因抛售持续下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/cash-turnover-in-indian-stock-market-slumps-as-selloff-continues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于经济增长放缓和全球波动加剧，印度股票市场现金部分的交易活动跌至一年多以来的最低水平，因为股票抛售持续进行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/cash-turnover-in-indian-stock-market-slumps-as-selloff-continues</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 03:16:00 GMT</pubDate>
